    "body": "Wouldn't it be cool to be able to do\r\n\r\n```coffee-script\r\ncreepersNearMe = client.find(\"entity.creeper\")\r\ndiamondsNearMe = client.find(\"block.diamond\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut also be able to chain\r\n\r\n```coffee-script\r\nclient.find(\"block.diamond\").dig(1000) # interval between digs otherwise you get kicked by bukkit\r\n\r\nclient.find(\"entity.creeper\").attack(100) # interval between attacks\r\n\r\nclient.find(\"block.diamond\").each (block) ->\r\n  if block.isWithinReach client.entity # 6 blocks\r\n    block.mine()\r\n\r\nclient.find(\"entity.skeleton\").walkTo({jumpEnabled: true}).attack()\r\n\r\nclient.find(\"object.chest\").interact().openWindow (window) ->\r\n  # window.title, #window.slots, etc.\r\n```\r\n\r\nJust some thoughts - let me know what you think.",
